  "instructions": [
    "Heat a wok or large skillet over medium-high heat. Add onion and garlic, stir-fry for about 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Add red and green bell peppers, broccoli, and mushrooms to the wok, stir-frying for another 3 minutes.",
    "Pour in soy sauce, fish sauce, sesame oil, and lime juice. Stir everything together well.",
    "Stir gently for an additional 2-3 minutes until all vegetables are heated through and flavors have melded together.",
    "Sprinkle with sesame seeds if desired before serving."
  ],
